value: Breeds in eastern Siberia north of Kamchatka and probably as far west as the Stanovoi Mountains; northern Kuril es (?). Winters from China, Korea and Japan south to the Philippines, Sunda Islands, Celebes, Moluccas, New Guinea and Australia.
